commit.title: [assumptions] Some refactoring on the printing code.
commit.message:
[assumptions] Some refactoring on the printing code.

This arose in the context of ejgallego/coq-serapi#86

Note that I am not sure this is the best way to it, as it feels like
we have quite a bit of duplication between the new `AssumptionCtx`
structure and `ContextObjectMap` [which by the way, shouldn't be a
set]?

Thus, I am submitting this PR as to gather more feedback and design
comments, instead of letting it rot in my SSD.
